name: BirdsSoundsforSleep
0:
”Alexa open birds sounds”
”Alexa ask birds sounds to play for 30 minutes”
”Alexa stop”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: birds sounds
des:
Put yourself to sleep with the calming sound of birds in the wild. Birds Sounds is the ultimate science-backed companion for relaxation, focus, and better sleep. 

All you need to do is say Alexa start Birds Sounds, and she will play the track for 30 minutes. This is a perfect skill to leave on while you are asleep, to use for relaxation and meditation, or to tune in and focus on your work.
